source.name: COMBINED VACANT ALLOCATED POSITIONS
source.description: The following list represents possible vacant positions within state agencies.  Due to changes in our workforce, challenges with up-to-date reporting and other factors, this list may not represent all of the vacancies or may list positions that have been filled since this data was collected.  There may be additional vacancies in the Department of Transportation; the Department of Conservation; the Department of Elementary and Secondary Education;  the Department of Public Safety (State Emergency Management Agency) and Department of Agricuture that are not represented here.
